snippet.textDisplay:
Streamlabs did NOT make OBS... OBS (Open Broadcaster Software) is made by the OBS Project, which is created and operated by Hugh Bailey, otherwhise known as Jim. OBS Studio is an open source software made and maintained by a stellar team over at GitHub, found here: https://github.com/obsproject

Streamlabs OBS is made on the OBS engine, made by the ones mentioned above, and is in my opinion frankly a straight ripoff... Proof of this can be found on their github page; https://github.com/stream-labs/streamlabs-obs/
right a the bottom where it states the following: "At its core, Streamlabs OBS is powered by the OBS engine. We want to thank all of the developers over at the OBS project for their years of tireless hard work, without which Streamlabs OBS wouldn't exist today."
